## Aggregate

| Metric | Value |
|---|---|
| Items planned | 5 |
| Items by priority | 1 critical, 2 major, 2 nit |
| Total expected words Δ | +160 |
| Source word count | 2150 |
| Projected new word count | 2310 |
| Target length window | 2000–2800 words (source: `overrides.<N+1>`) |
| Target-length flag | `within_target` |

The `Target-length flag` MUST be one of:

- `within_target` — projected count falls within `[min_words, max_words]` (inclusive).
- `exceeds_max` — projected count > `max_words`. Operator SHOULD decline items to land within budget.
- `under_min` — projected count < `min_words`. Operator SHOULD expand scope or accept under-budget delivery.
- `no_target` — no `target_length` is resolved for `v{N+1}` (source `"none"`); flag is informational only.
